   "body" : "Currently, the check for downloading a block is different here than it is in the parallel block fetch code, which means that we always request the full block when we could be using the compact block. This commit\r\nallows the compact block received to be utilized.\r\n\r\nAs a future improvement, we can add logic to allow the TXs in the latest block to be utilized also, saving them from being re-fetched due to not being in the mempool.",
